br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 決一不可</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:13:30.000Z","msg":"講得岩阿手足 推！"},{"pid":"6821e3c80bb9ab80e5b07240ed5479748832731e","tid":1467674,"uid":287387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:14:28.000Z","msg":"絕對未輸<br />\n絕對未輸<br />\n絕對未輸<br />\n絕對未輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n檢討改進<br />\n檢討改進<br />\n檢討改進<br />\n檢討改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要有檢討改進，就可以拉大同藍絲/popo的區別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b48841d4bf92fe93197f70fa4cc7b74f04f897","tid":1467674,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:17:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d3eebbd830ae8d47fb04d0150c0ec00c93a590c","tid":1467674,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:18:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"09c8a8843a4069accf84ee7b28837bae958993a1","tid":1467674,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fe54bf8416a545bf849b40c1df5c8f607333949e","tid":1467674,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:30:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"79a633b86a4cfdacfa2216ddd922580706b0d8e2","tid":1467674,"uid":48427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:35:02.000Z","msg":"無論係和理非定勇武打機場牌都好work,點解唔可以繼續打，<br />\n<br />\n小數人員換巨大成效，罷工都係為損害香港運作，迫機場又比塞鐵對圍內香港人反感度無咁高<br />\n<br />\n定又想番金鐘守夏愨龍和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b8f30f6383be28eebfb94e7fcf637c5b4964a2","tid":1467674,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79a633b86a4c